flowchart LR
  A[Agent (Claude Code / Cursor / custom)] -->|LLM API calls| P[Context Gateway Proxy
  - tracks tokens
  - compresses tool outputs
  - precomputes history compaction]

  subgraph Compression
    T[Tool output] --> IC[Intent-conditioned compressor
    (condition on tool call intent)] --> CT[Compressed tool output]
    CT --> P
    H[Conversation history] --> BG[Background compaction at threshold
    e.g., 75%] --> CH[Compacted history]
    CH --> P
  end

  P -->|Forward request| L[LLM Provider API
  (OpenAI/Anthropic/Ollama/Bedrock)]

  P --> LOG[JSONL logs
  - history_compaction.jsonl
  - tool_output_compression.jsonl
  - telemetry.jsonl]

  %% Optional escape hatch
  A -.->|expand() / fetch original output| P
